                "name": "Stage 4",
                "subtype": "affliction_stage",
                "text": "6d6 poison damage and controlled (1 round). A creature that dies while infected with creeping death immediately releases a burst of spores as if using the cythnophorian's Spore Cloud ability. If the corpse is not burned, it rises as the host of a new cythnophorian 12 hours later.",
