            "name": "Spore Cloud",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The cythnophorian emits a cloud of toxic spores, exposing all creatures within a 15-foot emanation to creeping death. The cythnophorian can't use Spore Cloud again for 1d4 rounds.",
